{"tid":2171110,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解冇人爭取過今年重啟選舉","createTime":"2020-08-23T17:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T04:44:18.000Z","uid":188810,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b4ef6f0d64337bc4017717e41c3bf9f5ef766529","tid":2171110,"uid":188810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:25:04.000Z","msg":"現在疫情都放緩<br />\n其實我地係唔係應該爭取返重啟立法會選舉<br />\n就算延遲亦都冇理由延一年<br />\n照現在個疫情發展, 延3個月都好夠啦<br />\n<br />\n將個重點搬返去重啟選舉, 百利而無一害<br />\n1. 選舉係共識, 不用再內鬥爭論去或留, 同埋只要有返選舉, 總唔總辭呢個問題已解決<br />\n<br />\n2. 大家有返個共同而明確的短期目標, 令大家團結<br />\n<br />\n3. 重握話語權, 延遲一年選舉係中共自把自為, 但奇怪係我地從來冇抗爭過就接受左, 仲要被帶風向內鬥, 將焦點推返去爭取盡快重啟選舉可以讓抗爭派拎返話語權, 唔好俾中共牽住走<br />\n<br />\n4. 五眼聯盟一早已經公開講左支持香港選舉, 我地企返出黎就等於響應返國際社會, 絕對比爭論去或留可以得到國際關注<br />\n<br />\n現屆立法會議員最有責任去帶領呢次抗爭, 何不順水推舟叫陣, 迫政府3個月內重啟選舉, 可以總辭作威脅, 亦可以講到明如果一日唔盡快重啟選舉, 入返議會都會用盡一切方法去癱瘓立法會(呢part應該由泛民自己去說服大眾, 說服唔到就應以總辭作最後手段)<br />\n<br />\n最後想講一句, 除左等國際打救, 香港人都應該積極d<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀, 人地見你咁順攤咩都接受, 仲有咩原因幫你<br />\n<br />\n既然政府都叫人排隊拎健康碼, 有咩理由唔可以排隊投票"},{"pid":"54be92b1c6fef3f95bafedca72cfb58b4d8dac1a","tid":2171110,"uid":188810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:25:28.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"e751bdc03fda27a416685ff5f1d895f31f3dddc0","tid":2171110,"uid":188810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:25:39.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"ec6b743a24f669407753efe0b4b0dbac0ae3ed05","tid":2171110,"uid":188810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:25:50.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"b3a895de3c4b69a902b1555940362a8d92b9cbb7","tid":2171110,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:52:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"943494837db9a3fddaedd11ff2c48c7ed7056bce","tid":2171110,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:52:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1b33c8df24883d80905922a614e15586bfcc512c","tid":2171110,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:52:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"148dca24d70963a372ba3701d425890fd0a05ed0","tid":2171110,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:02:01.000Z","msg":"立會選舉<br />\n如期舉行"},{"pid":"f36a1c7562ea50f465d0beeca6f03974a3f25bfc","tid":2171110,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫推"},{"pid":"f99f50a871d73263edc4b46da609370dbb8b5e26","tid":2171110,"uid":108631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:07:41.000Z","msg":"可以全民檢驗同健康碼 但唔可以投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad2d36c4d8df3010c700a593f1cab2b79886f80","tid":2171110,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T19:29:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還返投票權比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9731e41c81a31bb815a3ad1db81d81b85520f8ef","tid":2171110,"uid":80182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T19:30:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a2604c3868ac7f1a4df3f8afdb4edad418e57d5","tid":2171110,"uid":188810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T01:43:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e159d631344894f43908843749d731c779f400c6","tid":2171110,"uid":15057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T02:01:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77ee0b1ddf2c4b2ecb63661d98546f889517515e","tid":2171110,"uid":205469,"l